vernac_cmds: Definition In (x: Z) (i: interv) : Prop := fst i <= x < snd i.
Lemma In_dec: forall x i, {In x i} + {~In x i}.
Lemma notin_range: forall x i, x < fst i \/ x >= snd i -> ~In x i.
Lemma range_notin: forall x i, ~In x i -> fst i < snd i -> x < fst i \/ x >= snd i.
Definition empty (i: interv) : Prop := fst i >= snd i.
Lemma empty_dec: forall i, {empty i} + {~empty i}.
Lemma is_notempty: forall i, fst i < snd i -> ~empty i.
Lemma empty_notin: forall x i, empty i -> ~In x i.
Lemma in_notempty: forall x i, In x i -> ~empty i.
Definition disjoint (i j: interv) : Prop := forall x, In x i -> ~In x j.
Lemma disjoint_sym: forall i j, disjoint i j -> disjoint j i.
Lemma empty_disjoint_r: forall i j, empty j -> disjoint i j.
Lemma empty_disjoint_l: forall i j, empty i -> disjoint i j.
Lemma disjoint_range: forall i j, snd i <= fst j \/ snd j <= fst i -> disjoint i j.
Lemma range_disjoint: forall i j, disjoint i j -> empty i \/ empty j \/ snd i <= fst j \/ snd j <= fst i.
Lemma range_disjoint': forall i j, disjoint i j -> fst i < snd i -> fst j < snd j -> snd i <= fst j \/ snd j <= fst i.
Lemma disjoint_dec: forall i j, {disjoint i j} + {~disjoint i j}.
Definition shift (i: interv) (delta: Z) : interv := (fst i + delta, snd i + delta).
Lemma in_shift: forall x i delta, In x i -> In (x + delta) (shift i delta).
Lemma in_shift_inv: forall x i delta, In x (shift i delta) -> In (x - delta) i.
Function elements_rec (hi: Z) {wf (Zwf lo) hi} : list Z := if zlt lo hi then (hi-1) :: elements_rec (hi-1) else nil.
Lemma In_elements_rec: forall hi x, List.In x (elements_rec hi) <-> lo <= x < hi.
Definition elements (i: interv) : list Z := elements_rec (fst i) (snd i).
Lemma in_elements: forall x i, In x i -> List.In x (elements i).
Lemma elements_in: forall x i, List.In x (elements i) -> In x i.
Variable f: forall (x: Z), {P x} + {Q x}.

Program Fixpoint forall_rec (hi: Z) {wf (Zwf lo) hi}: {forall x, lo <= x < hi -> P x} + {exists x, lo <= x < hi /\ Q x} := if zlt lo hi then match f (hi - 1) with | left _ => match forall_rec (hi - 1) with | left _ => left _ _ | right _ => right _ _ end | right _ => right _ _ end else left _ _ .
assert (x = hi - 1 \/ x < hi - 1) by omega.
Definition forall_dec (P Q: Z -> Prop) (f: forall (x: Z), {P x} + {Q x}) (i: interv) : {forall x, In x i -> P x} + {exists x, In x i /\ Q x} := forall_rec P Q f (fst i) (snd i).
Function fold_rec (hi: Z) {wf (Zwf lo) hi} : A := if zlt lo hi then f (hi - 1) (fold_rec (hi - 1)) else a.
Lemma fold_rec_elements: forall hi, fold_rec hi = List.fold_right f a (elements_rec lo hi).
Definition fold {A: Type} (f: Z -> A -> A) (a: A) (i: interv) : A := fold_rec A f (fst i) a (snd i).
Lemma fold_elements: forall (A: Type) (f: Z -> A -> A) a i, fold f a i = List.fold_right f a (elements i).
Hint Resolve notin_range range_notin is_notempty empty_notin in_notempty disjoint_sym empty_disjoint_r empty_disjoint_l disjoint_range in_shift in_shift_inv in_elements elements_in : intv.
